<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="passion-n">passion <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pæʃn/    美 /'pæʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>激情；热爱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One should always be full of passion in his life no matter how old he is.
无论多大岁数，人应该总是在生活中充满激情。</p><footer>2015 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm very familiar with the history of my home city, and have a <strong>passion for</strong> history.
我非常熟悉我家乡的历史，而且酷爱历史。</p><footer>外研新选必④ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>passionate /ˈpæʃənət/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The secret to a good career is finding something that you <strong>are passionate about</strong>.
职业生涯成功的秘诀在于找到你所热爱的。</p><footer>人教新选必④ – 5</footer></div></div>